Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.07,0:22:53.26,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Flames that run down through my veins
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.60,0:22:57.61,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}I will make this city burn
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.82,0:23:01.97,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}We’re not planning to return
