Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.26,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Forgive me for letting you down
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.01,0:23:27.92,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Forgive me for letting you down again
