Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.25,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}為了你我能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:15.49,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}堅持你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:19.14,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果不再對我期待
